@@ -0,0 +1,78 @@
+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
+<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
+    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
+    android:layout_width="match_parent"
+    android:layout_height="match_parent"
+    android:paddingBottom="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
+    android:paddingLeft="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
+    android:paddingRight="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
+    android:paddingTop="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
+    tools:context="edu.hzuapps.androidworks.homeworks.Net1314080903135.Net1314080903135Activity"
+    android:background="#101450">
+
+    <Button
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="@string/button_zip"
+        android:id="@+id/button_zip"
+        android:layout_marginBottom="38dp"
+        android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
+        android:onClick="@android:string/ok"
+        android:clickable="true" />
+
+    <Button
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="@string/button_search"
+        android:id="@+id/button2"
+        android:layout_alignTop="@+id/button_zip"
+        android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
+        android:clickable="true" />
+
+    <ProgressBar
+        style="?android:attr/progressBarStyleHorizontal"
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:id="@+id/progressBar"
+        android:indeterminate="false"
+        android:background="#fdfefd"
+        android:layout_centerVertical="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
+        android:layout_alignRight="@+id/imageView"
+        android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/imageView" />
+
+    <TextView
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
+        android:id="@+id/textView"
+        android:background="#cbf8c6"
+        android:text="浏览"
+        android:layout_below="@+id/progressBar"
+        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
+        android:layout_marginTop="60dp"
+        android:layout_alignRight="@+id/button_zip"
+        android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/button_zip" />
+
+    <ImageView
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:id="@+id/imageView"
+        android:src="@drawable/net1314080903135title" />
+
+    <Button
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="@string/button_cancel"
+        android:id="@+id/button_cancel"
+        android:layout_alignBottom="@+id/button2"
+        android:layout_alignParentRight="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentEnd="true"
+        android:clickable="true"
+        android:onClick="@android:string/cancel" />
+
+</RelativeLayout>
